description:
Naudia Nyce, aka "Athena," got a little more then
she
bargained for from the
newcomer Calico. Calico, in her first match, used
her
strength and limited
skill to get the point lead going into the 3rd
round.
On the other hand, Athena is just a touch crazed,
and from out
of nowhere went into a
berserk sexual rage that cannot be described in
words alone. She dominated
RD3 and went on to fuck the poor Kitten almost to
tears. We now know that if you lose to Athena,
there are serious consequences.
title: Athena (0-1) Ranked 13th
